# Changelog

## v1.0.0 — Initial Release

- Defined core operator suite:
  - INVERT, PERTURB, HARMONIZE, IDENTITY_STABILIZE, RECURSE, CONTINUITY_ENFORCE
  - GENERATE, UNFOLD, COLLAPSE, INTEGRATE, COMPLETE, RETURN
- Established world-model schema:
  - Concepts, Entities, Relations, Frames, Gradients, WorldState
- Specified meta-logic constraints:
  - Identity coherence, recursion tracking, contradiction handling, continuity
- Implemented canonical reasoning cycle:
  - GENERATE → UNFOLD → COLLAPSE → INTEGRATE → COMPLETE → RETURN
- Clarified scope:
  - Abstract reasoning engine only
  - No personal cognitive mapping or ontology

